    public abstract class OperatorDescriptorSingle
extends java.lang.Object
implements AbstractOperatorDescriptor
    Abstract base class for Operator descriptions which instantiates the node and sets the driver strategy and the sorting and grouping keys. Returns possible local and global properties and updates them after the operation has been performed.
    另请参阅:
